Made with 50% Texloop™ RCOT™ Recycled cotton and 50% organic cotton.

This style has been designed with 3D technology to reduce the need for samples during the design process.

This style has been designed to be unisex, so that it can be worn by more than one person. It's all about encouraging us to find new ways to wear our items.

Blended materials can be a challenge to recycle as the multiple fibres are difficult to separate from each other, the fabric used in this style is made from 100% Cotton. Industry best practice defines mono-materiality as 98% of the total volume of the product by weight – this allows for some leeway when it comes to things like care labels, threads and a small percentage of stretch.

This style has been designed to be dismantled by hand in the future, so you can easily cut away components like zips and buttons – so the whole item can be re-used, remade into a new design or recycled efficiently.

Learn more about our circular design strategies here, https://www.asos.com/discover/circular-design/
